# AI Speaking Coach

An AI-powered English Speaking Coach built using Python, Whisper, Ollama, and Llama 3.

## Features

- Speech Recording
- Speech to Text Conversion
- Grammar Correction
- Fluency Scoring
- Progress Tracking
- Score Statistics
- PDF Report Generation
- Session History Storage

## Technologies Used

- Python
- OpenAI Whisper
- Ollama
- Llama 3
- ReportLab
- SoundDevice

## Project Structure

AI_Speaking_Coach/

├── speaking_coach.py

├── speech_to_text.py

├── ai_corrector.py

├── voice_test.py

├── history.txt

├── scores.txt

└── Speaking_Report.pdf

## How to Run

1. Install Python
2. Install Ollama
3. Pull Llama 3

```bash
ollama pull llama3
```

4. Install dependencies

```bash
pip install whisper sounddevice scipy reportlab ollama
```

5. Run

```bash
python speaking_coach.py
```

## Features Demonstration

- Record speech
- Analyze grammar
- Get fluency score
- Track improvement
- Generate PDF reports

